<bookmark xml-lang="en-US" branch="hid/SW:CHECKBOX:TP_OPTLOAD_PAGE:CB_AUTO_UPDATE_CHARTS" id="bm_id3154684" localize="false"/>
<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3159149" xml-lang="en-US" level="4" l10n="U" oldref="22">Charts</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3150768" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="24"><ahelp hid="SW:CHECKBOX:TP_OPTLOAD_PAGE:CB_AUTO_UPDATE_CHARTS">Specifies whether to automatically update charts. The<emph> Charts </emph>option is automatically activated if the <emph>Fields</emph> box has been marked.</ahelp></paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3151176" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="U" oldref="35">Caption</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3153367" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="36">Defines the settings for captions in tables, graphics, frames and OLE objects that have been inserted into a text document.</paragraph>
<bookmark xml-lang="en-US" branch="hid/SW_CHECKBOX_TP_OPTLOAD_PAGE_CB_CAPTION" id="bm_id3145750" localize="false"/>
<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3152597" xml-lang="en-US" level="3" l10n="U" oldref="37">Automatic</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3154147" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="38"><ahelp hid="SW_CHECKBOX_TP_OPTLOAD_PAGE_CB_CAPTION">Specifies that the objects selected in the <emph>Caption</emph> dialog (to open click the <emph>...</emph> button) are formatted as they are defined there.</ahelp></paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3150103" xml-lang="en-US" level="3" l10n="U" oldref="39">Object selection</paragraph>
<bookmark xml-lang="en-US" branch="hid/SW_PUSHBUTTON_TP_OPTLOAD_PAGE_PB_OPTIONS" id="bm_id3153954" localize="false"/>
<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3145272" xml-lang="en-US" level="3" l10n="U" oldref="40">...</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3146121" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="41"><ahelp hid="SW_PUSHBUTTON_TP_OPTLOAD_PAGE_PB_OPTIONS">The<emph> Object selection </emph>button opens the <emph>Caption</emph> dialog where you can make default settings for inserted objects of different types.</ahelp><comment>UFI: test if still in m55 after gt09 CWS</comment></paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3146976" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="U" oldref="46">Settings</paragraph>
<bookmark xml-lang="en-US" branch="hid/SW_LISTBOX_TP_OPTLOAD_PAGE_LB_METRIC" id="bm_id3152578" localize="false"/>
<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3153364" xml-lang="en-US" level="3" l10n="U" oldref="31">Measurement unit</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3146147" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="32"><ahelp hid="SW_LISTBOX_TP_OPTLOAD_PAGE_LB_METRIC">Specifies <link href="text/shared/00/00000003.xhp#metrik" name="Unit of Measure">unit of measure</link> for text documents.</ahelp></paragraph>
<bookmark xml-lang="en-US" branch="hid/SW_METRICFIELD_TP_OPTLOAD_PAGE_MF_TAB" id="bm_id3154729" localize="false"/>
<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3154944" xml-lang="en-US" level="3" l10n="U" oldref="33">Tab stops</paragraph>
